&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;About Boomi and What Makes Us Special&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Are you ready to work at a fast-growing company where you can make a difference?&amp;nbsp;Boomi, the data activation company for AI, powers the agentic enterprise by bringing data to life across the business. The award-winning&amp;nbsp;Boomi Enterprise Platform is the active data foundation that delivers essential agentic infrastructure enabling organizations to drive agentic transformation and&amp;nbsp;harness the power of AI with secure, scalable connectivity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Trusted by over 30,000 customers and supported by a network of 800+ partners, Boomi helps organisations of all sizes achieve agility, efficiency, and innovation at scale.&amp;nbsp;At Boomi, you’ll work with world-class people and industry-leading technology. We hire trailblazers with an entrepreneurial spirit who can solve challenging problems, make a real impact, and want to be part of building something big. If this sounds like a good fit for you, check out&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.boomi.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.boomi.com/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1782843859988000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3Yitd6hYQcya0j0B5k0__J&quot;&gt;boomi.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; or visit our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://boomi.com/company/careers/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://boomi.com/company/careers/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1782843859988000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2W_0H5BboonDUat_xHGW0d&quot;&gt;Boomi Careers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;page to learn more.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AI &amp;amp; Business Transformation Lead drives Boomi&#39;s strategic customer engagements at the executive level. This role translates Boomi&#39;s Agentic AI capabilities into business solutions and investment cases that justify significant capital allocation to present at Exec Level. Core responsibilities include advising global enterprises on AI and platform strategy, partnering with sales leadership to accelerate pipeline, and establishing best practices for data activation and AI-led transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role sits within Boomi&#39;s GTM Center of Excellence, which is responsible for design thinking, AI innovation, value selling methodology, and customer transformation outcomes. The successful candidate will build and maintain C-suite relationships, lead AI workshop sessions for customers, partners, and prospects, and actively differentiate Boomi across the market- with analysts, thought leaders, and key accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise C-suite stakeholders on AI and platform strategy, directly aligning Boomi&#39;s data activation &amp;amp; Agentic AI capabilities to their most critical business priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead commercial strategy for strategic pursuits, conducting executive-level discovery and developing insight-driven narratives that reframe investment decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Construct rigorous business cases linking Boomi&#39;s platform to measurable P&amp;amp;L impact, including NPV, IRR, and payback period modelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales teams to drive new and expansion revenue, contributing to account planning and embedding AI GTM strategy across key accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and operationalise value realization frameworks in coordination with Customer Success and Professional Services to validate outcomes post-sale&lt;/li&gt;
